snippet.title: Seacurity Breach Level Editor Trailer
snippet.description:
Seacurity Breach is a 3D tower defense game with a twist! We embrace verticality, ragdoll effects and a unique unit design. All wrapped in a beautiful low-poly graphical style. Expand your gameplay by testing yourself against a multitude of fan-created maps.

Check out the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/906660/Seacurity_Breach/

Follow us on social media for more updates:
https://twitter.com/SeacurityBreach/
https://www.facebook.com/SeacurityBreach/
